preference.name: CATIA_V4_checkin_generate_vis_data_priority
preference.preference_description: The scheduling priority for Catia V4 to JT check-in and/or save translations. The valid values of this preference are 0,1,2, and 3 corresponding to OFF, low, medium, and high priority. If this preference is not specified, no visualization data will be generated for check-in and/or save.
